      <title>耶伦表示，美国不会接受中国进口商品，从而摧毁新产业</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/yellen-meets-with-chinas-central-bank-chief-presses-case-excess-capacity-2024-04-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周一警告中国，华盛顿不会接受新产业因中国进口产品而遭受重创，她结束了为期四天的会议，敦促北京控制过剩的工业产能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/yellen-meets-with-chinas-central-bank-chief-presses-case-excess-capacity-2024-04-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 02:57:15 GMT</pubDate>
